<blockquote>
 <br> \(f(x) = {$a}x \) if \( x \leq $a \),
 <br> \(f(x) = x^2 \) if \( x \gt $a. \)
</blockquote>
<p>");


TEXT(EV3(<<'EOT'));
Let
$displayedfunc
$PAR
