$BR
\(\displaystyle{\lim_{x \rightarrow C^{-}} f(x)}\) = \{ans_rule(10)\}
$BR
\(\displaystyle{\lim_{x \rightarrow C^{+}} f(x)}\) = \{ans_rule(10)\}
$PAR
